title: Best of the Program | 10/26/22
description:
Glenn and Stu discuss the disgusting and arguably inhumane debate between Senate candidates Dr. Oz and John Fetterman, exposing the Democrats' apathetic feelings toward mentally unfit candidates. Glenn takes calls from his listeners to gauge how they're feeling with the midterms approaching. Glenn previews his latest podcast with Arizona gubernatorial candidate Kari Lake.
